CFA charterholder. Prior to joining Thornburg, he served as a senior credit analyst with H.I.G.
Capital in Miami, Florida, where he specialized in distressed debt investments and credit driven
special situations. Christian began his career in the investment banking division of Lehman
Brothers and later spent several years working on the high yield research desk at Lehman Brothers.
